description:
Darkness Radio welcomes the new year with Supernatural News & ParaShare Glitch in the Matrix Edition!

Dave & Tim uncover some unusual stories this week, McCartney is still communicating with George Harrison in an unconventional way, Tucker Anderson wants his UFO disclosure NOW, Professional Mediums lost to a control group in a psychic test, something creepy is living in the air ducts of a hospital in Brisbane, PLUS your stories in ParaShare and THE RETURN OF THEATER OF THE MIND!
